    <text>
        <body resp="#CM">
            <div type="letter_wrapper">
                <div corresp="#surface-1">
                    <div type="letter"><handShift hand="#h1"/>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline>
                                From <placeName ref="#PVAT">Piazza del Vaticano</placeName>, <date xml:id="dt1" when="1849-04-29">April 29, 1849</date>
                            </dateline>
                            <lb/>
                            <lb/>
                            <salute>
                                To the <choice>
                                        <abbr>Cmdr.</abbr>
                                        <expan><orgName ref="#CLE">Commander</orgName></expan>
                                    </choice> of the Legion of Emigrants
                            </salute>
                            <lb/>
                            <lb/>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The Minister of War, with the dispatch of the
                            <lb/>
                            27th of this month, entrusted to me the command
                            <lb/>
                            of the 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Brigade, which includes
                            <lb/>
                            your <orgName ref="#LE">Legion</orgName>.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The urgency of the moment requires that we <choice>
                                <sic>insen<lb break="no"/>diamo</sic>
                                <corr>lay siege</corr>
                            </choice> immediately, and therefore today
                            <lb/>
                            without fail you must be found with your
                            <lb/>
                            troops in <placeName ref="#PSMT">Piazza Santa Maria in<lb/>Trastevere</placeName>
                            and all communication lines.
                            <lb/>
                            <lb/>
                            Health and fraternity
                        </p>
                        <closer>
                            <salute>Yours,</salute>
                            <signed><persName ref="#GAR">G. Garibaldi</persName></signed>
                            <p xml:id="stamp-placeholder"/>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div corresp="#surface-2">
                    [see physical note]
                </div> 
                <div corresp="#surface-3">
                    <p>[physical marks]</p>
                </div> 
                <div corresp="#surface-4">
                    <p xml:id="phys1">[physical marks]</p>
                    <p xml:id="seal1">[seal]</p>
                    <ab type="address" facs="#address">
                        <handShift hand="#h1"/>
                        <p>
                            To the <orgName ref="#CLE">Commander of the Legion of Emigrants</orgName>
                            <lb/>
                            in <placeName ref="#ROM">Rome</placeName>
                        </p>
                    </ab>
                    <p xml:id="phys2">[physical marks]</p>
                    <p>
                        <handShift hand="#h2"/>
                        <persName ref="#GAR">Giuseppe Garibaldi</persName> from <placeName ref="#NIZ">Nice</placeName>
                        <lb/>
                        Filibuster, Corsair, General of the Republican troops
                        <lb/>
                        during the siege of Rome in 1849,
                        <lb/>
                        now in America once again,
                        <lb/>
                        a man of courage and audacity.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div> 
